title: Ep 216 - Jetha In London
shortDesc: The society celebrates Ganesh Chaturti together while Jetha is in London  on his business. What happens next? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 217 - Daya misses Jethalal
shortDesc: While Jetha is on a business trip in London, Daya misses him and remembers all the good times they had before he left. Watch this episode to find out what happens next.

title: Ep 218 - Ethnic Day Contest At Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: On the account of Ganesh Chaturti, Gokuldham society arranges an ethnic day contest. The prize is given to the winner by Randeep Huda. Who is the winner? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 219 - Garba At Gada Electronics
shortDesc: Daya comes to look after Jetha's shop to look after the business. She comes up with a sales pitch which becomes a big hit. What is this new scheme? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 221 - Dayas Shayari On Jethalal
shortDesc: While playing the Couple's Sharyari game, Daya recites an emotional poem on her husband, saying that she misses him. Meanwhile, Jethalal calls her from London to give her a surprise. What is this surprise? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 222 - Robbery At Gokuldham!
shortDesc: Tappu Sena returns from school to witness the donation box open. They all scream and alarm their parents about the robbery. How will the Gokuldham residents solve this problem?

title: Ep 223 - Remembering Funny Incidents From The Past.
shortDesc: Gokuldham has a special guest at Ganesh Chaturthi puja and all the residents take a moment to remember everyone's funny incidents from the past. they also realize how these little incidents brought all the residents to make one big family.

title: Ep 224 - Daya Misses Jethalal
shortDesc: Jetha is still in London on business and Daya on the other hand,  Daya is unable to sleep as she's missing her husband.

title: Ep 225 - Jethalal Returns From London
shortDesc: As Daya starts the aarti, Jetha makes an entry back home. Everyone in the colony is excited to have him back. Watch this episode to know what happens next.

title: Ep 226 - Gifts From London
shortDesc: Now that Jetha has come home, Tappu demands that he gets his gifts immediately. So, Jetha decides to unpack and distribute everyone's gifts to them.

title: Ep 227 - No Gift For Iyer.
shortDesc: Daya and Jetha decide to visit their fellow residents and give them their gifts. Will everyone like their presents? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 228 - Jethalal Back To His Lazy Practices.
shortDesc: Jethalal is back to his lazy practices now that he's back from London. He uses the difference in timings as his excuse to sleep longer but, will that work? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 229 - Jethalals New Look
shortDesc: Jethalal is back from London and has returned with a new look. What does everyone else think about his new look? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 230 - Jethalals New Friend From London
shortDesc: A lady visits the Gada family and asks Daya to pass on a gift to Jetha. Everyone in the society is surprised to have this visitor. But, what is Daya's opinion on this?

title: Ep 231 - Jethalals Intervention
shortDesc: Daya lets her friends know about the guest she had. Shocked to hear the news from Daya, the ladies tell their husbands about the new visitor who in turn decide to have an intervention for him.
